layout: base
title: "Weeks · BibleProject Plan"
description: "Weekly overview of BibleProject reading plan with links to each day."
permalink: "/weeks/"
---
<header class="mb-5 md:mb-6">
  <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-[28px] font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Weekly Reading Plan</h1>
  <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600">Browse the reading plan by week.</p>
  <p class="mt-2.5 text-sm text-slate-500">Tip: Use your browser's find to jump to a specific week number.</p>
</header>

<div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4">
  {% for w in plan.weeks %}
    <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-3 shadow-sm hover:shadow transition-shadow">
  <div class="font-medium text-slate-900">Week {{ w.weekNumber }}{% if w.hasJustice %} <span class="text-sm" title="Justice scripture present this week">⭐</span>{% endif %}</div>
      <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Day {{ w.days[0].day }} - Day {{ w.days | last | map: "day" }}</div>
      <div class="mt-2"><a class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-2.5 py-1.5 text-white text-xs font-medium hover:bg-blue-500" href="/week/{{ w.weekNumber }}/">Open Week</a></div>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
